There are 5 guards total, Watchman Halv and Mylz are the ones you want to be killing.The other three are more or less unkillable solo,at least it doesnt pay <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Anyway,Halv has around 1600hp,is lvl 35 and doubles for 92 max each plus kick/bash.If you get in 2 shocks of swords and a blaze,you even get exp from him at 48(slllloooowwww tho).He has low MR and usually some caster sitting by him,waiting to kite him around.<br>
Mylz has about the same hp,is lvl 35 as well,but doubles for up to 102 each plus kick/bash again.However he is HIGHLY magic resistant,dont expect your spells to stick unless you have Malismented him.Due to this,he is almost never camped.<br>
Loot is crappy,up to 5pp moneywise,and always a shortsword and wooden shield,at times FS weapons.<br>
<br>
Its better to get kos with gnomes in their enclave as with dwarves and their ports <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Steamfont is a good place to solo if you cant find a group,but dont spend the entire time from 44 to 48 there. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Aquamini</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#333333>(10/14/00 2:37:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlevels4950.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=115.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Gnome=ish faction</span><hr size=1> sounds cool but you might wanna do your jboots quest before you go after gnomes.. Hasten Bootstrutter happens to be a gnome.. just a little advice for anyone that cares..<br>
